FBIS4-861 "drafr075_a_94005" FBIS-AFR-94-075 Daily Report 18 Apr 1994 CENTRAL AFRICA Rwanda RPF Denies Belgians Attacked RTLM Radio RPF Denies Belgians Attacked RTLM Radio EA1804183094 (Clandestine) Radio Muhabura in Kinyarwanda to Rwanda 1030 GMT 18 Apr 94 EA1804183094 (Clandestine) Radio Muhabura Kinyarwanda BFN [Excerpts] The Belgian contingent of the UN Assistance Mission in Rwanda is returning home tomorrow. [passage omitted] Now government troops are saying that the Belgians are helping the Rwanda Patriotic Front in the war. They claim that the bomb that hit the Radio Television Libre des Milles Collines [RTLM] was the work of the Belgians. All these are pretexts. It has been clear all along that the dictatorship has been defeated, so in return they massacred people. [passage indistinct]
